 R←Test_Search_030(stopFlag batchFlag);n;⎕TRAP;html
⍝ Search for "Foo" everywhere, then narrow down: just APL, comments, text and finally all possible combination.
 ⎕TRAP←(999 'C' '. ⍝ Deliberate error')(0 'N')
 R←∆Failed

⍝ Preconditions
 1 #._Fire.Fire.Run 0
 n←#._Fire.Fire.GUI.n

 #.⎕SHADOW'TMP'
 'TMP'#.⎕NS''
 #.TMP.⎕FIX'⍝ Leading comment "Foo"' ':Class Class1' 'Hello←{' 'Foo←1' '''Foo''' '}' ':EndClass' '⍝Foo'
 #.TMP.⎕FIX'⍝ Leading comment "Goo"' ':Class Class2' 'Hello←{' 'Goo←1' '''Goo''' '}' ':EndClass' '⍝Goo'
 #.TMP.⎕FIX'⍝ Leading comment "Foo"' ':Namespace Namespace1' 'Hello←{' 'Foo←1' '''Foo''' '}' ':EndNamespace' '⍝Foo'
 #.TMP.⎕FIX'⍝ Leading comment "Goo"' ':Namespace Namespace2' 'Hello←{' 'Goo←1' '''Goo''' '}' ':EndNamespace' '⍝Goo'
 #.TMP.⎕FX'r←Fns1 dummy' '⍝ Foo' 'Foo←1' 'r←''Foo'''
 #.TMP.⎕FX'r←Fns2 dummy' '⍝ Goo' 'Goo←1' 'r←''Goo'''
 #.TMP.⎕FX'r←FnsJustCode dummy' 'Foo←1' 'r←1 2 3'
 #.TMP.⎕FX'r←FnsJustComment dummy' '⍝Foo←1' 'r←1 2 3'
 #.TMP.⎕FX'r←FnsJustText dummy' 'r←''⍝Foo←1'''
 #.TMP.⎕FX'r←FnsJustCommentAndText dummy' '⍝ Foo' 'r←''All about Foo' 'a←''Foo'''
 #.TMP.⎕FX'r←FnsJustCodeAndComment dummy' 'Foo←''1 2 3''' '⍝ All about Foo' 'r←1 2 3'
 #.TMP.⎕FX'r←FnsJustCodeAndText dummy' 'Foo←''1 2 3''' 'r←''Foo'''
 #.TMP.vars1←'Foo' 'Goo' 'Zoo'
 #.TMP.vars2←'Foo;Goo;Zoo'
 #.TMP.vars3←'This and that'
 #.TMP.vars4←'''Foo''' 'Goo' 'Zoo'
 'NS'#.TMP.⎕NS''
 #.TMP.NS.⎕FX'r←Fns_A dummy' '⍝ Foo' 'Foo←1' 'r←''Foo'''
 #.TMP.NS.⎕FX'r←Fns_B dummy' '⍝ Goo' 'Goo←1' 'r←''Goo'''

 n.SearchFor.Text←'Foo'
 n.LookIn.Text←'#.TMP'
 n.Case.State←0

⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝ Search everywhere: APL code, comments, text
 {}∆Select n.StartBtn
 ∆Process n.Form
 →PassesIf 14=⍴n.HitList.Items
 →PassesIf 14=#._Fire.Fire.G.NoOfObjects
 →PassesIf 27=#._Fire.Fire.G.NoOfHits
 →PassesIf 27=↑+/n.HitList.ReportInfo[;#._Fire.Fire.GUI.hc.Hits]

 ⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝ Search just Code, no Vars
 n.(Comments Text Vars).State←0
 {}∆Select n.StartBtn
 ∆Process n.Form
 →PassesIf 7=⍴n.HitList.Items
 →PassesIf 7=#._Fire.Fire.G.NoOfObjects
 →PassesIf 7=#._Fire.Fire.G.NoOfHits
 →PassesIf 7=↑+/n.HitList.ReportInfo[;#._Fire.Fire.GUI.hc.Hits]

⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝ Search just Comments
 n.(APL_Code Text).State←0
 n.Comments.State←1
 {}∆Select n.StartBtn
 ∆Process n.Form
 →PassesIf 7=⍴n.HitList.Items
 →PassesIf 7=#._Fire.Fire.G.NoOfObjects
 →PassesIf 9=#._Fire.Fire.G.NoOfHits
 →PassesIf 9=↑+/n.HitList.ReportInfo[;#._Fire.Fire.GUI.hc.Hits]

⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝ Search just Text
 n.(APL_Code Comments).State←0
 n.Text.State←1
 n.Vars.State←1
 {}∆Select n.StartBtn
 ∆Process n.Form
 →PassesIf 10=⍴n.HitList.Items
 →PassesIf 10=#._Fire.Fire.G.NoOfObjects
 →PassesIf 11=#._Fire.Fire.G.NoOfHits
 →PassesIf 11=↑+/n.HitList.ReportInfo[;#._Fire.Fire.GUI.hc.Hits]

⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝ Search just Code and Comments
 n.(Text Vars).State←0
 n.(APL_Code Comments).State←1
 {}∆Select n.StartBtn
 ∆Process n.Form
 →PassesIf 10=⍴n.HitList.Items                              ⍝ Because the namespace and the fns within the namespace...
 →PassesIf 10=#._Fire.Fire.G.NoOfObjects                    ⍝ ... count twice because there is text outside fns/opr!
 →PassesIf 16=#._Fire.Fire.G.NoOfHits
 →PassesIf 16=↑+/n.HitList.ReportInfo[;#._Fire.Fire.GUI.hc.Hits]

⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝ Search just Code and Text
 n.(Comments Text).State←0
 n.(Code Text).State←1
 n.Vars.State←1
 {}∆Select n.StartBtn
 ∆Process n.Form
 →PassesIf 12=⍴n.HitList.Items
 →PassesIf 12=#._Fire.Fire.G.NoOfObjects
 →PassesIf 18=#._Fire.Fire.G.NoOfHits
 →PassesIf 18=↑+/n.HitList.ReportInfo[;#._Fire.Fire.GUI.hc.Hits]

⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝⍝ Search just Comments and Text
 n.APL_Code.State←0
 n.(Comments Text).State←1
 {}∆Select n.StartBtn
 ∆Process n.Form
 →PassesIf 13=⍴n.HitList.Items                              ⍝ Because the namespace and the fns within the namespace...
 →PassesIf 13=#._Fire.Fire.G.NoOfObjects                    ⍝ ... count twice because there is text outside fns/opr!
 →PassesIf 20=#._Fire.Fire.G.NoOfHits
 →PassesIf 20=↑+/n.HitList.ReportInfo[;#._Fire.Fire.GUI.hc.Hits]

⍝ Tidy up
 CloseFire

 R←∆OK
